1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 32=

3
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:16,879
Come, everyone.

4
00:00:16,879 --> 00:00:18,039
Please come inside.

5
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:22,000
So it's the Grandmaster
of the Northern Martial Alliance,

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,000
along with the Guardians.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Look at this...

8
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,079
This is just my humble thatched hut.

9
00:00:27,187 --> 00:00:28,787
Feel free to look around.

10
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:30,960
Well, Dongfang Bai,

11
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,719
you've set so many traps
in the courtyard.

12
00:00:33,720 --> 00:00:34,719
Who are you trying to keep out?

13
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:36,679
To keep out my enemies, of course.

14
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:39,159
But just now,

15
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,640
I didn't realize it was you all.

16
00:00:41,810 --> 00:00:42,679
It's a misunderstanding.

17
00:00:42,679 --> 00:00:43,880
A complete misunderstanding.

18
00:00:45,359 --> 00:00:47,560
These things of yours are quite strange.

19
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:50,560
I usually just enjoy researching some

20
00:00:50,799 --> 00:00:52,799
Western dials, screw cores, and such.

21
00:00:53,359 --> 00:00:54,679
I don't have any other hobbies.

22
00:00:55,359 --> 00:00:56,119
What is this?

23
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,640
This? This is a sleeve arrow.

24
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,439
It can fire a powerful bolt.

25
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,439
Be careful, be careful!

26
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,480
This can really hurt someone.

27
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,159
My dear wife,

28
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:09,079
you almost cost my life just now.

29
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:10,380
Then, I could just get a new one.

30
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:11,920
Dongfang Bai,

31
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:13,920
you really have quite a lot

32
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,799
of weird gadgets here.

33
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,799
I'm a solitary man

34
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,439
who doesn't like socializing,

35
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:20,560
so I just tinker around with these things.

36
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:26,400
We're here because
we have something to ask you.

37
00:01:27,362 --> 00:01:30,150
(Token: Ministry of Justice,
Probe Corps, Mao Jixian)

38
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,599
Wenrong.

39
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,280
Buyu,

40
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:46,719
are you alright?

41
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,640
I'm fine.

42
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,920
I'm back.

43
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:54,239
From now on,
the matters of the Mao family

44
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:56,680
will be borne by me alone.

45
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,760
How will you bear them?

46
00:01:59,319 --> 00:01:59,920
I...

47
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,519
Buyu,

48
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:03,120
listen to my advice.

49
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:05,920
Marry Wushuang.

50
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:09,520
I know it's hard for you to accept,

51
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,840
but hasn't Chu Yunchang
already been married?

52
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,319
She has failed you.

53
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,719
Why do you still struggle like this?

54
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:20,639
Right now, the Mao family
has already fallen into decline.

55
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,759
Without the help of the Luo family,

56
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:24,039
it will be hard to rise again.

57
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:27,560
I hope you can consider the big picture

58
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,639
and agree to the marriage with Wushuang.

59
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,960
Please.

60
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:38,560
Wenrong, what are you doing?

61
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:42,599
This was Father's only dying wish.

62
00:02:44,110 --> 00:02:45,360
Get up first, then we'll talk.

63
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:53,200
(Token: Ministry of Justice,
Probe Corps, Mao Jixian)

64
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,039
I'll agree to it, then.

65
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:03,479
Come.

66
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:06,319
Yours.

67
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,080
Are you afraid I've poisoned it?

68
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:29,919
We share responsibility for the death
of your twin brother, Dongfang Qing.

69
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:31,190
Don't tell me you didn't know.

70
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,599
I have long since retired.

71
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:38,919
I have long
since let go of worldly affairs.

72
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:42,599
My brother didn't listen to me
and brought trouble upon himself.

73
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,439
He got what he deserved.

74
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,280
If I wanted to seek revenge,

75
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,120
wouldn't I have come for you long ago?

76
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,439
Lord Shen

77
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:51,439
has told you my hiding place

78
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:54,080
simply because he wants me to tell

79
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:55,680
the truth about what happened back then.

80
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,280
So,

81
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,560
there's no need to be so wary.

82
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,439
I harbor no ill will.

83
00:04:11,039 --> 00:04:14,319
I wonder if you could tell us the truth
of what happened back then?

84
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:22,000
I've known for a long time

85
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,000
that this matter
couldn't be hidden forever.

86
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:26,160
Since you've all come here,

87
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:29,839
I might as well tell you the truth

88
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,920
from 30 years ago.

89
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:35,680
More than 30 years ago,

90
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,362
your grandfather, Chu Zhongtian,

91
00:04:37,362 --> 00:04:39,199
was still a handsome young man.

92
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,800
Young and reckless,

93
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:43,639
he stole the imperial treasure,
the Gold-Threaded Armor.

94
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:46,839
The court ordered the Gate Bureau
to solve the case within a deadline.

95
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:50,000
Luo Shixun was then a constable
of the Gate Bureau's Arrest Corps.

96
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,040
(Young Luo Shixun)
He went to Jiangnan by imperial decree to investigate.

97
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:55,680
(Young Chu Zhongtian)
Luo Shixun pursued Chu Zhongtian for three days and nights.

98
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,920
They accidentally fell into a cave

99
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,199
and were trapped inside.

100
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:02,399
As they say,
out of blows, friendship grows.

101
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,439
They matched wits and strength daily

102
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,920
and actually became friends.

103
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:08,880
One of us is in the government,
and the other is an outlaw.

104
00:05:09,290 --> 00:05:10,319
If we combine our efforts

105
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:12,320
to root out those
malignant elements one by one,

106
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,439
wouldn't that be great?

107
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:17,079
From then on, the duo of
the soldier and thief worked together,

108
00:05:17,079 --> 00:05:18,279
solving many strange cases.

109
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,800
During that time,

110
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,920
the two were almost
inseparable and shared everything.

111
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:26,199
For a while, it became
a legendary tale in the martial world.

112
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:32,040
Luo Shixun received
one promotion after another.

113
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,319
To show his gratitude,

114
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:35,639
he reported the deeds
of the Sacred Hand Sect to the court.

115
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:38,560
Because Chu Zhongtian
restrained his disciples,

116
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:41,200
forbidding them from bullying the weak
and encouraging heroic acts,

117
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:42,980
(Benevolent Martial World)
they were commended by the court.

118
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:47,079
But Luo Shixun grew jealous.

119
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,920
He got Chu Zhongtian drunk

120
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:52,680
to trick him into revealing
the location of the Sacred Token.

121
00:05:53,687 --> 00:05:56,007
Then, using the hands
of the Southern Four Great Thieves,

122
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,879
he successfully stole the Sacred Token.

123
00:05:58,199 --> 00:06:00,680
(Token)
Then, he poisoned them to keep them silent.

124
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:10,439
(Young Dongfang Qing)
Because Dongfang Qing wasn't deeply poisoned,

125
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:13,600
he snatched the Silver Sacred Token
and narrowly escaped.

126
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,920
(Wanted Poster)
But he was framed by Luo Shixun,

127
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:18,160
leading him to be
wanted across the land.

128
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:20,162
(Wanted Poster)

129
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,279
No wonder Dongfang Qing
sought me out for revenge,

130
00:06:23,279 --> 00:06:24,759
but lured me to the Gate Bureau.

131
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:27,199
It seems he wanted to use me

132
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:28,879
to make a deal with Luo Shixun.

133
00:06:28,879 --> 00:06:31,360
That brother of mine
was far too conceited.

134
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:34,920
How could a man
like Luo Shixun be easily trusted?

135
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:37,160
I suspect my brother's recent death

136
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,160
is also connected to him.

137
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,399
So, what happened after that?

138
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,879
Afterward, Chu Zhongtian
lost the Sacred Token.

139
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,120
In the martial world,

140
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,879
he lost all face.

141
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,199
Filled with remorse,

142
00:06:49,439 --> 00:06:51,110
and with thieves rising up everywhere,

143
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,120
no one respected
the rules of the Martial Alliance

144
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,040
anymore.

145
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,680
The martial world fell into chaos again.

146
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:57,439
Chu Zhongtian was devastated.

147
00:06:57,550 --> 00:06:59,300
He searched everywhere
for the Sacred Token.

148
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,160
How could he have known

149
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:04,000
that it was his own friend
who betrayed him?

150
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:07,360
In the end,
unable to find the Sacred Token,

151
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,199
he died in grief.

152
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:12,319
So Grandfather
misplaced his trust in a traitor.

153
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,920
Now, those two Sacred Tokens

154
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:16,600
should be in
the scoundrel Luo Shixun's hands.

155
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,560
But currently,

156
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,120
he already has
two tokens in his possession,

157
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,360
yet he hasn't made a move.

158
00:07:24,650 --> 00:07:25,600
What is he waiting for?

159
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:30,199
Perhaps he has
an even bigger conspiracy.

160
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:31,770
That makes sense.

161
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,120
If left unchecked,

162
00:07:33,170 --> 00:07:35,560
it could very well cause
a bloodbath in the martial world.

163
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:38,000
When that time comes,
the court will surely intervene.

164
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,759
The Martial Alliance

165
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,680
would also face total destruction.

166
00:07:42,462 --> 00:07:43,621
What a sinister plot.

167
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,800
Auntie, Uncle,

168
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,360
we must find a way

169
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,920
to expose Luo Shixun's scheme.

170
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:06,639
Yu, were you looking for me?

171
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:14,959
Yes.

172
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,959
What is it?

173
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:20,600
Wushuang.

174
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:23,560
I...

175
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,360
Just say it.

176
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:32,720
I'm here to propose to you.

177
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,480
I hope you'll accept.

178
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:40,879
You

179
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,679
are proposing to me?

180
00:08:47,475 --> 00:08:48,875
Are you being serious?

181
00:08:49,050 --> 00:08:49,971
If you don't agree,

182
00:08:50,350 --> 00:08:51,480
just pretend I never said it.

183
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,240
I didn't say I wouldn't agree.

184
00:08:58,799 --> 00:09:01,120
Fine, I'll agree to it.

185
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:04,120
Thank you, Wushuang.

186
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,440
My sister will visit your home
to propose in a few days.

187
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:25,720
(He finally proposed.)

188
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:33,759
(But why don't I feel happy?)

189
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,799
(Skyscraper Cliff Thatched Hut)
Stay and enjoy a few more days.

190
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:40,279
Don't head down the mountain yet.

191
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,440
Chang,

192
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:42,960
are you really not coming with us?

193
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,799
Although we've seen through
the scoundrel's plot,

194
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,437
we still haven't found

195
00:09:47,437 --> 00:09:48,960
a proper way to deal with it.

196
00:09:49,279 --> 00:09:51,879
So I plan to go into seclusion
on the mountain for a while.

197
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,637
Once we find a proper solution,

198
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,925
we'll make the evidence
of his crimes public.

199
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:01,080
What about you, Zhizhi?

200
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:03,000
I don't want to go back either.

201
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:05,200
I want to stay and study under a master.

202
00:10:06,679 --> 00:10:08,759
What master? What are you studying?

203
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,000
I want to stay here

204
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,440
and learn those fun things
from Mister Dongfang.

205
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,399
Wonderful!

206
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:16,879
I happen to get along
quite well with Miss Zhizhi.

207
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:19,120
I've been worried that I'd have
no one to pass my life's work to.

208
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,879
In that case, I'm willing to take
Miss Zhizhi as my apprentice.

209
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:23,440
Great! Then, I'll kowtow to you.

210
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:24,240
Master!

211
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:25,080
Good girl.

212
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:25,960
Rise, please.

213
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,759
Auntie, Uncle,

214
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,360
you two head down first.

215
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:31,260
It'll be five or six days
at the earliest,

216
00:10:31,279 --> 00:10:32,840
fifteen days at the latest.

217
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:34,600
Then we'll head down and meet you

218
00:10:34,610 --> 00:10:35,830
to go to the Capital together.

219
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:41,440
You're so disrespectful.

220
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,080
What's wrong? Why so happy?

221
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:44,960
Grandfather,

222
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:47,480
Mao Buyu proposed.

223
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:52,240
Your wish has finally come true.

224
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:54,320
Grandfather,

225
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:57,320
you must reinstate
Mao Buyu to his original post.

226
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,360
You also need
to clarify this matter publicly.

227
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,639
I don't want people
in our circle gossiping

228
00:11:01,639 --> 00:11:03,240
when I get married.

229
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:05,399
Look at you.

230
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:07,399
You're already protecting him
before the wedding.

231
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:08,000
Let go.

232
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:09,279
Grandfather!

233
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,120
Don't worry.

234
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:13,200
Since Mao Buyu is becoming
my grandson-in-law,

235
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,960
I will certainly look after him.

236
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,960
Thank you, Grandfather!

237
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,440
Grandfather, you're the best.

238
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,200
Have some tea.

239
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,000
Wushuang,

240
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,279
congratulations!

241
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:22,120
You finally got what you wanted.

242
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:25,480
If you hadn't been
causing trouble here every day,

243
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,960
my wish would have come true long ago.

244
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,120
How can you say that?

245
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:30,919
Everything I did was
for the sake of the Luo family,

246
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:31,519
Grandfather.

247
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:33,000
Nonsense.

248
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:35,000
Look at the two of you.

249
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,600
Bickering the moment you meet.

250
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:39,440
That's because Luo Wuxia
is always siding with outsiders.

251
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,600
You've got it all wrong.

252
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,639
I'm doing this to earn karma
for the Luo family.

253
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:46,000
Look, our family
has been constables for generations.

254
00:11:46,279 --> 00:11:47,639
It looks glamorous on the surface,

255
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,620
but in reality,
our hands are stained with blood.

256
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:50,919
I'm worried that,

257
00:11:50,919 --> 00:11:53,039
sooner or later, retribution will come.

258
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,600
No, no.

259
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:04,240
I just had some
reflections from this trip

260
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:06,080
to Chengdu, that's all.

261
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,159
Give it a rest.

262
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,399
Stop reflecting.

263
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,559
You're useless at everything,

264
00:12:09,559 --> 00:12:10,759
but number one at talking nonsense.

265
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:11,480
Get out of here.

266
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,380
I have serious business
to discuss with Grandfather.

267
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,360
Hey, you...

268
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,275
I...

269
00:12:18,399 --> 00:12:19,279
Fine, I'm leaving.

270
00:12:20,190 --> 00:12:21,200
I'm leaving, Grandfather.

271
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:23,087
I won't see you out.

272
00:12:49,575 --> 00:12:53,600
♪Donning a mask to hide my heart♪

273
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:55,120
Why are you running so fast?

274
00:12:55,519 --> 00:12:56,039
I...

275
00:12:56,690 --> 00:12:58,125
I came to return your handkerchief.

276
00:13:01,212 --> 00:13:04,837
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

277
00:13:05,525 --> 00:13:08,700
♪A love so deep,
yet destiny so fleeting♪

278
00:13:08,759 --> 00:13:09,590
You embroidered this?

279
00:13:09,662 --> 00:13:12,375
♪This fervor is buried deep within♪

280
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:14,679
Impressive.

281
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:16,039
You did a great job.

282
00:13:17,337 --> 00:13:20,837
♪To the moment we first met♪

283
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:25,362
♪Casting aside all obsession
just to be with you♪

284
00:13:25,487 --> 00:13:29,162
♪Despite countless ordeals♪

285
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,320
It's so sour!

286
00:13:32,639 --> 00:13:33,440
You have one too.

287
00:13:34,039 --> 00:13:35,200
Have one.

288
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:35,919
No.

289
00:13:37,412 --> 00:13:41,400
♪Worlds apart, I wait for our reunion♪

290
00:13:41,587 --> 00:13:45,562
♪But I'll spend my life
keeping you safe♪

291
00:13:45,575 --> 00:13:48,675
♪Lies and vows,
let them stay in the past♪

292
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,679
This is a peace talisman
I got from the temple.

293
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,879
You go out fighting
and killing every day.

294
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,600
It really makes me worry.

295
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,720
From now on,

296
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,200
we are finished.

297
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:13,263
♪Taking off the mask,
revealing the true heart♪

298
00:14:13,412 --> 00:14:16,512
♪Can't bear to keep acting anymore♪

299
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,279
Can't catch me.

300
00:14:17,937 --> 00:14:20,750
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

301
00:14:21,162 --> 00:14:24,537
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

302
00:14:24,639 --> 00:14:25,720
You can't run away now.

303
00:14:25,762 --> 00:14:29,400
♪A love so deep,
yet destiny so fleeting♪

304
00:14:29,487 --> 00:14:32,512
♪This fervor is buried deep within♪

305
00:14:32,975 --> 00:14:37,312
♪I long for it so much,
I crave to return♪

306
00:14:37,350 --> 00:14:40,762
♪To the moment we first met♪

307
00:14:40,837 --> 00:14:45,375
♪Casting aside all obsession
just to be with you♪

308
00:14:45,425 --> 00:14:49,338
♪Despite countless ordeals♪

309
00:14:49,537 --> 00:14:53,325
♪I can't untie the knot in your heart♪

310
00:14:53,525 --> 00:14:57,075
♪I end up creating another knot instead♪

311
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,970
Are you really not going
to wait for Yunchang?

312
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,159
Please inform Chang for us, Miss Shen.

313
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,300
We'll head to the Capital first
to check things out.

314
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:04,399
Fine.

315
00:15:04,799 --> 00:15:05,840
Take care on your journey.

316
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:13,080
Dear, in a little while, we...

317
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,000
What's wrong?

318
00:15:17,279 --> 00:15:18,159
What is it, dear?

319
00:15:21,519 --> 00:15:23,000
I'm not feeling very well.

320
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,120
Not well? Let me see.

321
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:28,879
How is it?

322
00:15:30,039 --> 00:15:30,799
Say something!

323
00:15:31,679 --> 00:15:32,879
You're expecting, dear!

324
00:15:35,679 --> 00:15:37,440
I'm pregnant?

325
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:43,879
That's wonderful.

326
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,000
Dear,

327
00:15:50,399 --> 00:15:51,720
have something to eat. Come.

328
00:15:56,679 --> 00:15:57,360
Dear,

329
00:15:58,400 --> 00:16:00,919
I feel like this child
has come at the wrong time.

330
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:02,639
Dear,

331
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,519
what do you mean by that?

332
00:16:05,799 --> 00:16:07,559
We were just about
to look for Luo Shixun

333
00:16:07,559 --> 00:16:08,820
to get revenge on the scoundrel.

334
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,759
But this child suddenly arrived.

335
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:13,519
I've said it before,

336
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:15,000
if I were to get pregnant,

337
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:17,000
I would want to live in seclusion.

338
00:16:17,110 --> 00:16:18,690
But now, the grudge hasn't been settled.

339
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,519
What should I do?

340
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:21,919
Dear,

341
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:24,200
just focus on nursing the pregnancy.

342
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:26,440
I will take care of the revenge myself.

343
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,279
No.

344
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,480
I must personally
avenge my father and brother.

345
00:16:30,559 --> 00:16:31,360
Dear,

346
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,519
why must you do this?

347
00:16:33,919 --> 00:16:35,919
Whether you act or I act,

348
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:37,320
it's all the same, isn't it?

349
00:16:37,399 --> 00:16:38,399
How can it be the same?

350
00:16:38,399 --> 00:16:39,480
Alright, alright.

351
00:16:40,039 --> 00:16:41,159
Don't worry, dear.

352
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,240
Don't upset the baby.

353
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:44,799
I don't care.

354
00:16:45,039 --> 00:16:46,590
I'm going back to the Capital regardless

355
00:16:46,710 --> 00:16:47,799
to reclaim the Sacred Token

356
00:16:47,799 --> 00:16:48,990
and kill Luo Shixun with my own hands.

357
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,039
Auntie, you must not.

358
00:16:51,279 --> 00:16:52,039
Chang,

359
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,759
you're back.

360
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:56,240
We originally planned
to return tomorrow,

361
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,720
but Die sent word

362
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:59,000
saying that you're expecting.

363
00:16:59,279 --> 00:17:00,679
So we came back today instead.

364
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,639
Congratulations.

365
00:17:03,559 --> 00:17:05,480
The first three months
are the most critical.

366
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,039
You both stay here at the Shen Manor.

367
00:17:07,039 --> 00:17:08,039
Don't go anywhere.

368
00:17:08,039 --> 00:17:09,039
Exactly.

369
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,559
Just focus on your pregnancy.

370
00:17:10,559 --> 00:17:12,119
Leave everything else to me.

371
00:17:12,359 --> 00:17:14,319
Uncle, you shouldn't take risks either.

372
00:17:14,559 --> 00:17:15,759
Auntie is pregnant,

373
00:17:15,759 --> 00:17:17,559
so you should stay by her side
to take care of her.

374
00:17:17,559 --> 00:17:19,400
If anything were to happen to you, then

375
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:21,319
what would happen to the unborn child?

376
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:23,759
If your auntie stays at the Shen Manor,

377
00:17:23,759 --> 00:17:25,090
everything will be perfectly safe.

378
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,480
Yes, Yunchang.

379
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:28,000
With Mrs. Mei at my home,

380
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,759
you and Squire Mei can rest easy.

381
00:17:30,319 --> 00:17:31,039
That won't do.

382
00:17:31,039 --> 00:17:32,000
I've already decided.

383
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,890
Zhizhi and I will return
to the Capital together

384
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:37,880
to avenge my father and grandfather,
and to take back the Sacred Token.

385
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:39,359
The two of you

386
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:42,000
will stay here and wait for the birth.

387
00:17:43,279 --> 00:17:44,319
Wait for the birth?

388
00:17:45,039 --> 00:17:46,759
That's still eight or nine months away.

389
00:17:47,039 --> 00:17:48,200
Exactly, Chang.

390
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,187
I can't just stay put here.

391
00:17:50,519 --> 00:17:51,880
I don't agree.

392
00:18:01,187 --> 00:18:04,462
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

393
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:07,375
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

394
00:18:07,875 --> 00:18:13,593
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

395
00:18:14,775 --> 00:18:18,095
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

396
00:18:18,225 --> 00:18:21,145
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

397
00:18:22,313 --> 00:18:27,553
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

398
00:18:28,775 --> 00:18:31,168
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

399
00:18:31,168 --> 00:18:34,818
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

400
00:18:34,887 --> 00:18:38,377
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

401
00:18:38,475 --> 00:18:41,450
♪To the ends of time♪

402
00:18:41,450 --> 00:18:44,825
♪The moon traces your face♪

403
00:18:45,012 --> 00:18:48,600
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

404
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:54,840
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

405
00:18:55,175 --> 00:18:58,390
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

406
00:18:58,675 --> 00:19:02,213
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

407
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:05,525
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

408
00:19:05,525 --> 00:19:08,625
♪On our way to forever♪

409
00:19:08,625 --> 00:19:12,475
♪The moon traces your face♪

410
00:19:12,475 --> 00:19:15,835
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

411
00:19:16,025 --> 00:19:21,985
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

412
00:19:23,062 --> 00:19:32,702
♪Just to be with you♪
